params:
ctx
left
top
width
height
aux

8.text:
ctx.arc(
    right - aux,
    top + aux,
    aux,
    Math.PI * 1.5,
    Math.PI * 2
)

10.text:
ctx.moveTo(left, bottom)
ctx.lineTo(left, top)
ctx.lineTo(right, top)
ctx.lineTo(right, bottom)

9.text:
ctx.arc(
    right + aux,
    bottom - aux,
    aux,
    Math.PI * 1.0,
    Math.PI * 0.5,
    true
)

6.text:
right = left + width
bottom = top + height

3.text:
ctx.arc(
    left - aux,
    bottom - aux,
    aux,
    Math.PI * 0.5,
    Math.PI * 0.0,
    true
)

7.text:
ctx.arc(
    left + aux,
    top + aux,
    aux,
    Math.PI * 1.0,
    Math.PI * 1.5
)

name: buildTabPath
